      "*": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b><a href=\"/Main_Page\" title=\"Main Page\">Home</a> * <a href=\"/People\" title=\"People\">People</a> * Martin Giepmans</b>\n</p>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:232px;\"><a href=\"http://old.csvn.nl/gallery16.html\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/thumb/d/da/Giepma18.jpg/230px-Giepma18.jpg\" width=\"230\" height=\"234\" class=\"thumbimage\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/d/da/Giepma18.jpg/345px-Giepma18.jpg 1.5x, /images/thumb/d/da/Giepma18.jpg/460px-Giepma18.jpg 2x\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/File:Giepma18.jpg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>Martin Giepmans <sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></div></div></div> \n<p><b>Martin Giepmans</b>,<br />\nwas a Dutch computer chess programmer, and author of the chess engines <a href=\"/SpiderChess\" title=\"SpiderChess\">SpiderChess</a> and <a href=\"/Anatoli\" title=\"Anatoli\">Anatoli</a>, both written in <a href=\"/Delphi\" title=\"Delphi\">Delphi</a>. Martin died from <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Cancer\">cancer</a> in October 2009 <sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup> <sup id=\"cite_ref-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup> . \n</p>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Forum_Posts\">Forum Posts</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Martin_Giepmans&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Forum Posts\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=388903\">A Delphi - WinBoard problem</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Martin Giepmans</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, September 24, 2004&#160;» <a href=\"/Delphi\" title=\"Delphi\">Delphi</a>, <a href=\"/WinBoard\" title=\"WinBoard\">WinBoard</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.open-aurec.com/wbforum/viewtopic.php?f=18&amp;t=49085\">A problem with my delphi engine in Windows XP</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Martin Giepmans</a>, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">Winboard Forum</a>, September 26, 2004</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=20636\">LMR?</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Martin Giepmans</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, April 12, 2008&#160;» <a href=\"/Late_Move_Reductions\" title=\"Late Move Reductions\">Late Move Reductions</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"External_Links\">External Links</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Martin_Giepmans&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: External Links\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.game-ai-forum.org/icga-tournaments/person.php?id=126\">Martin Giepmans's ICGA Tournaments</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Martin_Giepmans&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: References\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\">Martin Giepmans, <a href=\"/ICT_2002\" title=\"ICT 2002\">ICT 2002</a>, Photo from <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://old.csvn.nl/gallery16.html\">2nd CSVN-Tournament 2002 Gallery</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-2\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.open-aurec.com/wbforum/viewtopic.php?f=2&amp;t=50486\">Martin Giepmans (Anatoli, SpiderChess) passed away</a> by <a href=\"/Olivier_Deville\" title=\"Olivier Deville\">Olivier Deville</a>, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">Winboard Forum</a>, October 15, 2009</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-3\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-3\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=30160\">Martin Giepmans (Anatoli, SpiderChess) passed away</a> by <a href=\"/Andres_Valverde\" title=\"Andres Valverde\">Andres Valverde</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, October 15, 2009</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div>\n<p><b><a href=\"/People\" title=\"People\">Up one level</a></b>\n</p>\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260301120255\nCache expiry: 86400\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.013 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.014 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 57/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 130/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 0/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 0/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 2/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%    0.000      1 -total\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key oscar70_mw1-mw_:pcache:idhash:5583-0!canonical and timestamp 20260301120255 and revision id 12193\n -->\n"
